FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]

    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[FirstName], [a].[ImageName], [a].[LastName]
    FROM [Actors] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ActorsId], [a0].[FilmsId], [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]

    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]

    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]

    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BirthDate], [t].[FirstName], [t].[ImageName], [t].[LastName], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Director], [t0].[Duration], [t0].[ImageName], [t0].[ReleaseDate], [t0].[Title]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[FirstName], [a].[ImageName], [a].[LastName]
    FROM [Actors] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ActorsId], [a0].[FilmsId], [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [Films] AS [f] ON [a0].[FilmsId] = [f].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ActorsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[FilmsId]

    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]

    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]

    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]

    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]

    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[FirstName], [a].[ImageName], [a].[LastName]
    FROM [Actors] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ActorsId], [a0].[FilmsId], [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [Films] AS [f] ON [a0].[FilmsId] = [f].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ActorsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[FilmsId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]

FROM [Films] AS [f]

    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[BirthDate], [a].[FirstName], [a].[ImageName], [a].[LastName]
    FROM [Actors] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ActorsId], [a0].[FilmsId], [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [Films] AS [f] ON [a0].[FilmsId] = [f].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ActorsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ActorsId], [t0].[FilmsId]

    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

FROM [Films] AS [f]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Description], [t].[Director], [t].[Duration], [t].[ImageName], [t].[ReleaseDate], [t].[Title], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Name], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[BirthDate], [t1].[FirstName], [t1].[ImageName], [t1].[LastName], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Description], [t2].[FilmId], [t2].[Stars], [t2].[Title], [t2].[UserId], [t2].[Id0], [t2].[Name], [t2].[Password], [t2].[Role]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[ActorsId], [a].[FilmsId], [a0].[Id], [a0].[BirthDate], [a0].[FirstName], [a0].[ImageName], [a0].[LastName]
    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Actors] AS [a0] ON [a].[ActorsId] = [a0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[Description], [r].[FilmId], [r].[Stars], [r].[Title], [r].[UserId], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[Name], [u].[Password], [u].[Role]
    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmsId], [t0].[GenresId], [t0].[Id], [t1].[ActorsId], [t1].[FilmsId], [t1].[Id], [t2].[Id]

FROM [Films] AS [f]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]

    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

    FROM [ActorFilm] AS [a]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

2024-05-29 23:57:07.611 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId], [t].[Id], [t].[Name]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmsId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [t].[FilmsId], [t].[GenresId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]

    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [f].[Id], [f].[Description], [f].[Director], [f].[Duration], [f].[ImageName], [f].[ReleaseDate], [f].[Title]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Id] = @__filmId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmsId], [f0].[GenresId], [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [FilmGenre] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [f0].[GenresId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmsId]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[FilmsId]

    FROM [Reviews] AS [r]
    LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [r].[UserId] = [u].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[FilmId]
